1) Load Image (Node): 确保其尺寸比例与 text2img 中选择的尺寸比例相同。

2) AIO Node: 选择预处理器。第一次运行时，可能需要一些时间......因为要从互联网上下载。

3) 加载与预处理器相匹配的 ControlNet 模型。

4) Apply ControlNet (Node):

Canny (Pre = CannyEdge):             Set "end_percent" at exactly 0.300

Depth (Pre = DepthAnythingv2):       Set "end_percent" at exactly 0.400

HED (Pre = HED):                     Set "end_percent" at exactly 0.200

OpenPose (Pre = DW):                 Set "end_percent" at exactly 0.300

NOTE: Use Ctrl+B to toggle on/off a node.
